long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension to make searching Youtube videos faster. Just enter 'Y' and press 'TAB' in the address bar and start searching. 

Suggested results are shown in the drop down menu . Select 'Show Video' to open the first search result in a new tab or select 'Show Search Results' to open the youtube search result page of the given query.
